tafsir[19]{c,v,t}:
  82,1,"Si kammu on fettii sabi tellaade Malayka en e mammba."
  82,2,"Si koode ɗe njanii ɗe carii."
  82,3,"Si maaje ɗe udditiraama ɗe njillandiri."
  82,4,"Si genaale ɗe leydi mum waylaama sabu ummitaade maaynooɓe wonnooɓe heen."
  82,5,"Oon ntuma kala fittaandu annda kondu ardinno e golle e kondu leelnuno tawa ndu gollaana ɗuum."
  82,6,"Eehey ma neɗɗanke keefeero;holko taki haɗa lunndoo joom ma tuma nde O muñan ma O yaawnaaki leptude ma e teddungal Makko?"
  82,7,"Oon gootnuɗo ma caggal nde a wonaani, O waɗ ma fotandirɗo terɗe poocciiɗ."
  82,8,"E kala mbaadi ndi O faalaa O takru ma, O neemanii ma sabu O waɗaani ma e mbaadi mbabba wollo waandu maa rawaandu wollo goɗɗum."
  82,9,"Huunde nde wonah no mbaadanirɗon nih-onon hoomtaaɓe- ko woni ko, ko on yeddooɓe ñalngu njoɓdi on ngollantaa mbo."
  82,10,"Na woodi e dow mon, malaykaaji deenooji golle mon."
  82,11,"Tedduɗi ka Alla, binnddoji golle mon."
  82,12,"Gannduɗi ko ngolloton e golle ɗi mbinndaɗe."
  82,13,"Pellet ɓeen heewa golle lobbe e ɗoftaare ina e neema duumiiɗo ñande darnga."
  82,14,"Pellet ɓe faajiraagal ina e yiite huɓɓatnde e dow mum en."
  82,15,"Hoɓe naatange ñande ñalngu njoɓdi."
  82,16,"ɓe ngonah wirnatooɓe yiite nge haa bada, ko woni kay ko toon ɓe caasata."
  82,17,"Hol ko anndin Ma-aan nelaaɗo-ñalngu njoɓñdi."
  82,18,"Refti hol ko anndin Ma ñalngu njoɓdi."
  82,19,"ñalngu ngu hay gooto waawah nafde hay gooto, huunde fof ko Alla woodani ñande heen, O firlitoo hono no O faalara, goɗɗo wo alah."
